value:
A decoration said to be placed in the entryway
of Hoshidan homes as a way of celebrating the
new year. It's an event item.

A lantern made of wood in the style of those
seen across Hoshido. The red color is said to
protect from catastrophes. It's an event item.

A red gate in the style said to be seen across
Hoshido, decorated with New Year's trappings
to celebrate coming change. It's an event item.

Used in Aether Raids to build structures that
are available for a limited time. If that period
has elapsed, these stones will be lost.
